The HI Growth Initiative, in just four years, has shown Hawaii is a viable place build competitive startups. A recent study by the University of Hawaii’s Economic Research Organization found 65 companies have been funded as a result of the HI Growth Initiative. The average capital investment from the HI Growth Initiative is $160,000 per company, representing a cumulative investment at the end of 2015 of $10.5 million. Companies on average have gone on to attract an additional $2 million in private funding for a total of $136 million: over 12X leverage on the state’s investment.

Description: 12 Bridges provides a cloud platform as a service for IoT and data analytics driven cloud services and applications services.
Headquarters Regions: West Coast, Western US
Full Description: Unleashing the business value of data. 12 Bridges is a software and services company providing a cloud platform as a service for IoT and data analytics-driven cloud services and applications services across multiple market segments, including but are not limited to, consumer and commercial appliances, transportation and logistics, health and wellness, and smart buildings, campuses, and cities. For connected sensor, device, and mobile app makers, our platform provides an end to end solution for adding cloud connectivity and data-driven service revenue streams to those devices that save time and money developing, deploying and operating an IoT product, while also enabling new revenue streams for their device data and context. For data and analytic-driven service providers, our platform provides an efficient and scalable path to access IoT or connected device data and end customer context for analytics to enable responsive service integration into those devices. The platform can be deployed in a vertically integrated fashion for customers who want to implement both the devices and the connected services, or it can be leveraged as a multi-sided market connecting device makers, data provider, service providers, and analytic or visualization app developers together both technically and commercially. The platform is cloud infrastructure agnostic, so customers can choose their preferred cloud infrastructure provider and avoid being locked in, or even deploy in a private data center.

Headquarters Regions: Greater Los Angeles Area, West Coast, Western US
Full Description: Md Saidul Islam (Bengali: মোঃ সাইদুল ইসলাম, born February 27, 1991) is a prominent digital artist and painter from Bangladesh. Saidul's exceptional talent and eye-catching artwork have gained him widespread recognition and admiration in his country. Saidul has made a significant impact on the local art scene, especially in the online space. His creations have drawn the attention and admiration of fellow artists, art lovers, and the general public. It has received both recognition and praise from these diverse audiences. Those who have had the pleasure of experiencing Saidul's work strongly feel a deep emotional connection with his art. His work serves as a source of inspiration, leaving a profound and enduring impact on viewers. Md Saidul Islam has specialized in painting portraits of legendary figures throughout his artistic life, expertly portraying their essence and personalities through his stunning brushstrokes. His deep dedication and passion have led him to create a renowned series of portrait paintings that include the respected founding father of the country, Bangabandhu Sheikh Mujibur Rahman, and his daughter, Sheikh Hasina Wazed, who is Bangladesh's longest-serving prime minister. These artworks have gained significant attention because of his exceptional talent for expressing the charisma and spirit of his subjects. The depths of their characters are conveyed in his artworks, which go beyond simple visual representation. Saidul's exceptional talent and constant dedication to his passion shine through his ability to breathe life into his subjects, creating mesmerizing and emotionally resonant artworks. Saidul started creating portraits of Bangabandhu Sheikh Mujibur Rahman in 2011, which marked the beginning of his artistic destination. He put a lot of effort into every brushstroke to improve his abilities and published his work on websites like Deviant Art Gallery. There, his talent began to attract the interest and attention of more and more admirers of his artistic skills. Saidul found the platform to be a useful venue for showcasing his abilities, getting noticed, and connecting with a growing audience. This moment was crucial in Saidul's artistic journey, motivating him to keep exploring and pushing the limits of his creativity. In 2018, Saidul took on the exciting challenge of portraying Prime Minister Sheikh Hasina through his art. With great skill and attention to detail, Saidul brought depth and emotion to his paintings, paying tribute to the significant contributions Prime Minister Sheikh Hasina has made to the nation. His artworks beautifully represent her inspiring leadership and stand as a tribute to her profound influence on society. A true artist at heart, beyond creating stunning works of art, Saidul has dedicated himself to spreading the ideals and ideology of Bangabandhu Sheikh Mujibur Rahman through the powerful medium of digital media. Saidul's artworks have contributed significantly to both offline and online campaigns for Bangladesh Awami League, the largest political party in Bangladesh. Numerous people have been touched by his art because it has the power to stir up emotions, incite inspiration, and spread important messages. The evolution of Md Saidul Islam's art is evidence of his everlasting commitment, talent, and ability to make his subjects come to life. He crafts a visual narrative that captures the true spirit and essence of legendary individuals through his influential and appealing artwork. Saidul's artwork does more than just represent people's faces; it awakens feelings and delivers compelling narratives. His talent and enthusiasm are shown in every brushstroke, which leaves a deep impression on viewers. As he continues to create more art, Saidul's influence in the field of the artistic medium grows, inspiring others and leaving a legacy that will endure for years to come.
